{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879196887,"sessionID":"ses_2855a7b1dffey50fYwwDatY1vT","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa610a10015WZYNIyH3traV5","messageID":"msg_d7aa5cb2d001R6GNjVukzFxoHC","sessionID":"ses_2855a7b1dffey50fYwwDatY1vT","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-ae159825d6af4a16b1f4c40595dc5169","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端 Specification\n\n## Module: sdk-python\n\n### HTTPClient Class\n\n#### Constructor\n\n```python\nclass HTTPClient:\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        base_url: str,\n        timeout: int = 30,\n        max_retries: int = 3,\n        headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None\n    ) -> None\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `base_url`: Base URL of the API service\n- `timeout`: Request timeout in seconds (default: 30)\n- `max_retries`: Maximum number of retry attempts (default: 3)\n- `headers`: Optional default headers to include in all requests\n\n#### Core HTTP Methods\n\n##### get\n\n```python\nasync def get(\n    self,\n    path: str,\n    params: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None,\n    headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None\n) -> Dict[str, Any]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `path`: API endpoint path\n- `params`: Optional query parameters\n- `headers`: Optional request headers\n\n**Returns:** Response data as dictionary\n\n**Raises:** `HTTPError`, `ConnectionError`, `TimeoutError`\n\n##### post\n\n```python\nasync def post(\n    self,\n    path: str,\n    data: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None,\n    json: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None,\n    headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None\n) -> Dict[str, Any]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `path`: API endpoint path\n- `data`: Optional form data\n- `json`: Optional JSON data\n- `headers`: Optional request headers\n\n**Returns:** Response data as dictionary\n\n**Raises:** `HTTPError`, `ConnectionError`, `TimeoutError`, `ValidationError`\n\n##### put\n\n```python\nasync def put(\n    self,\n    path: str,\n    data: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None,\n    json: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None,\n    headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None\n) -> Dict[str, Any]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `path`: API endpoint path\n- `data`: Optional form data\n- `json`: Optional JSON data\n- `headers`: Optional request headers\n\n**Returns:** Response data as dictionary\n\n**Raises:** `HTTPError`, `ConnectionError`, `TimeoutError`, `ValidationError`\n\n##### delete\n\n```python\nasync def delete(\n    self,\n    path: str,\n    headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None\n) -> Dict[str, Any]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `path`: API endpoint path\n- `headers`: Optional request headers\n\n**Returns:** Response data as dictionary\n\n**Raises:** `HTTPError`, `ConnectionError`, `TimeoutError`\n\n## Data Models\n\n### HTTPConfig\n\n```python\nclass HTTPConfig(BaseModel):\n    base_url: str\n    timeout: int = 30\n    max_retries: int = 3\n    headers: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None\n    verify_ssl: bool = True\n```\n\n### HTTPError\n\n```python\nclass HTTPError(Exception):\n    status_code: int\n    message: str\n    details: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n```\n\n### RetryConfig\n\n```python\nclass RetryConfig(BaseModel):\n    max_retries: int = 3\n    backoff_factor: float = 1.0\n    retry_on_status_codes: List[int] = [429, 500, 502, 503, 504]\n```\n\n## Exception Hierarchy\n\n```\nSDKHTTPException\n├── HTTPError\n├── ConnectionError\n├── TimeoutError\n└── ValidationError\n```\n\n## Features\n\n### Authentication Support\n- API key authentication\n- Bearer token authentication\n- Custom authentication headers\n\n### Retry Logic\n- Configurable retry strategy\n- Exponential backoff\n- Status code-based retry triggers\n\n### Error Handling\n- Structured error responses\n- Detailed error messages\n- Request/response logging (optional)\n\n### Connection Pooling\n- Keep-alive connections\n- Connection limits\n- Timeout management","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-029/spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-029/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-029/spec.md","time":{"start":1775879196873,"end":1775879196885}}}}
